; Coverage for history.cc find_price without target commodity
; --market without --exchange uses find_price(source, moment, oldest)
; which finds the best price for the source commodity regardless of target

P 2024/01/01 AAPL $150.00

2024/01/15 Buy
    Assets:Brokerage    10 AAPL
    Assets:Checking

test bal --market Assets:Brokerage --now 2024/02/01
            $1500.00  Assets:Brokerage
end test
